China Media Group President and Editor-in-Chief, Shen Haixiong, has delivered an online video message introducing the world to a state-of-the-art 5G live streaming studio. In his video message, Shen invited media colleagues from all over the world to use the studio, built on a high-speed train being used at the 2022 Beijing Winter Olympics. He said China is ready for the Games and let us be together for a shared future.